text: Santiago Peña Palacios (; born 16 November 1978) is a Paraguayan politician and economist. He became the 52nd President of Paraguay on 15 August 2023. He was the Minister of Finance of Paraguay from 2015 to 2017. He is a member of the Colorado Party. He ran for president before in 2018. ==References== Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:Paraguayan politicians
